results.title: X-Men: Days of Future Past (Trade Paperback)

textObjects.text: "Re-live the legendary first journey into the dystopian future of 2013 - where Sentinels stalk the Earth, and the X-Men are humanity's only hope...until they die! Also featuring the first appearance of Alpha Flight, the return of the Wendigo, the history of the X-Men from Cyclops himself...and a demon for Christmas!? "

textObjects.text: On the mean streets of the Marvel Universe, the kid gloves come off.
